{"lemma":"كَدُّ","slug":"كَدُّ","root":"ك.د.د","root_slug":"ك-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36719","n36724"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to work hard, to toil, to exert oneself, to slog","examples":[{"text":"وَمَا كَانَ مِنَ ٱلْحَيَوَانِ صُلْبًا يَرْعَى‭‬ فِي ٱلْمَرَاعِي ٱلْيَابِسَةِ ٱلصُّلْبَةِ وَيَكُدُّ‬ فِي ٱلْأَعْمَالِ ٱلصَّعْبَةِ‭‬ فَإِنَّهَا أَصْلَبُ وَأَبْطَأُ ٱسْتِمْرَاءً","english":"What there is of sturdy animals grazing the dry and harsh pastures and exerting themselves in hard works, they are tough and tardy (when to be digested)."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make weary, to tire, to goad","examples":[{"text":"لَا بُدَّ أَنَّهُ شَيْءٌ مَوْجُودٌ، مِنْ حَجَرٍ وَتُرَابٍ وَمَاءٍ وَسَمَاءٍ، وَلَيْسَتْ مِثْلَمَا تَهُومُ فِي رَأْسِهِ ٱلْمَكْدُودِ","english":"It was certainly something real, of stones, earth, water, and sky, not as it slumbered in his troubled mind."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to scratch off, to scrape","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَدَّ (kadda) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb","uncountable","usually"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"toil, fatigue, assiduity","tags":["uncountable","usually"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mortar","tags":["obsolete","rare","uncountable","usually"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Aramaic כּדּא (kaddā, “pot, pitcher”), ultimately from Old Tamil 𑀓𑀺𑀡𑁰𑀝𑀺 (kiṇṭi, “pitcher pot”). Doublet of قَادُوس (qādūs)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36719","headword_ar":"كُدَّ","root":"kd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He toiled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, vehement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in work;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he worked laboriously;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fatigued himself, and hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in his work. (L.) [You say]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bijad~ika laA bikad~ika","text_ar":"بِجَدِّكَ لَا بِكَدِّكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"By thy good fortune, not by thy toil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"are things attained. A proverb. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tajoEalo Eayo$ahumaA kad~F","text_ar":"لَا تَجْعَلْ عَيْشَهُمَا كَدًّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make not the life of them two a toil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, from a trad.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmasaAy^ilu kad~N yakad~u bihaA","text_ar":"المَسَايِلُ كَدٌّ يَكَدُّ بِهَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ajulu wajohahu","text_ar":"الرَّجُلُ وَجْهَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Petitions are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a cause of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispiriting: a man thereby impairs the brightness of his countenance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, from a trad.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~ahu","text_ar":"كَدَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K, aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He required of him toil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severity in work,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persevering"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constant exertion in striving to do a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in seeking a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aktd~hu","text_ar":"اكتدّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astkd~hu","text_ar":"استكدّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fatigued"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wearied"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * L;) namely, a beast, and a man, &c.: (L;) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dak~ahu","text_ar":"دَكَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he plied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pressed him, plied"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pressed him hard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"harassed him, in constant work which he imposed upon him, so as to fatigue"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weary him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, L.) See also"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2595},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fatigued"},{"kind":"text","text":"his tongue with speaking and his heart with thinking. (A, L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He exerted himself perseveringly, assiduously, constantly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incessantly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in striving to do, effect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplish, a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in seeking"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sustenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the means of subsistence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pointed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a sign, with the finger,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K,) like as the beggar does. (S.) [It is also trans.] El-Kumeyt says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"ganiytu falamo A^arodudokumu Einoda bigoyapK\n                      \n                     \n                        waHujotu falamo A^akodudokumu biAlA^aSaAbiEi"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I was rich, and I did not repel you on an occasion of exigency; and I was in want, and I did not point at you with the fingers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, L.) ―         -b2-  ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kud~uwniY faA_in~iY mukid~N","text_ar":"كُدُّونِى فَاـِنِّى مُكِدٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ask ye of me; for I give"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"only"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when asked."},{"kind":"text","text":"Said by Ibn-Hubeyreh. (A [but in my copy of that work, the first word is written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kid~uwniY","text_ar":"كِدُّونِى"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":".] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He scratched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scraped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he scraped off"},{"kind":"text","text":"a soil from a garment: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he scratched perseveringly"},{"kind":"text","text":"his head, and his skin, with his nails. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~N","text_ar":"كَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He combed"},{"kind":"text","text":"his head. (K, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kad~a","text_ar":"كَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a beast)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trod"},{"kind":"text","text":"the ground with his hoofs. (A, * L.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kd~hu","text_ar":"كدّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pulled"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew it out"},{"kind":"text","text":"(i. e. a solid or a fluid thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aktd~hu","text_ar":"اكتدّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, K.)"}],"source_refs":["L","S","K","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n36724","headword_ar":"كَدٌّ","root":"kd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of 1, q. v. ―         -b2-  as a subst.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mortar in which things are pounded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bruised;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haAwanN","text_ar":"هَاوَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haAwuwnN","text_ar":"هَاوُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}